abSan v1.0
Philip Barrett
Chicago, August 2013
*******************************************

This folder contains the R package abSan, an R implementation of Abreu & Sannikov's
algorithm for computing the equilibria of repeated games.  This is described in 
detail in their 2013 Theoretical Economics paper "An algorithm for two-player 
repeated games with perfect monitoring"

